Record match_envs (f: meminj) (cenv: compilenv) (e: env) (le: temp_env) (m: mem) (lo hi: block) (te: env) (tle: temp_env) (tlo thi: block) : Prop := mk_match_envs { me_vars: forall id, match_var f cenv e m te tle id; me_temps: forall id v, le!id = Some v -> (exists tv, tle!id = Some tv /\ Val.inject f v tv) /\ (VSet.mem id cenv = true -> v = Vundef); me_inj: forall id1 b1 ty1 id2 b2 ty2, e!id1 = Some(b1, ty1) -> e!id2 = Some(b2, ty2) -> id1 <> id2 -> b1 <> b2; me_range: forall id b ty, e!id = Some(b, ty) -> Ple lo b /\ Plt b hi; me_trange: forall id b ty, te!id = Some(b, ty) -> Ple tlo b /\ Plt b thi; me_mapped: forall id b' ty, te!id = Some(b', ty) -> exists b, f b = Some(b', 0) /\ e!id = Some(b, ty); me_flat: forall id b' ty b delta, te!id = Some(b', ty) -> f b = Some(b', delta) -> e!id = Some(b, ty) /\ delta = 0; me_incr: Ple lo hi; me_tincr: Ple tlo thi }.
